<font size=4>
Instructions: ./pr08 with options 
 </td>
<td align=center>
<font size=4>
 Options are: <br>
 screen input_image cluster_size<br>
 floyd input_image [optional:numberToReduce] <br>
 uniform input_image [optional:numberToReduce] <br>
 random input_image [optional:numberToReduce]  <br>

</td>
</tr>



